$ %APPDATA%\Microsoft\Templates

`%APPDATA%\Microsoft\Templates` (and its subdirectories?) contain templates for → Microsoft/Office applications that are available for a given user.

This directory and its subdirectories


sa:
   Templates that are available for all users are stored under → Windows/dirs/Program-Files/Microsoft-Office/root/Templates[`%PROGRAMFILES%\Microsoft Office\root\Templates`].

  → Windows/dirs/Program-Files/Microsoft-Office/root/Templates
